text: Kidryachevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kidryachevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 487 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kidryachevo
